OL,3,CPolice urge drivers to avoid closed
OL,4,Cstretch of M5 after serious crash
OL,6,FGloucestershire Police are urging
OL,7,Fdrivers to avoid the area around M5
OL,8,Fjunctions 11 and 9 northbound
OL,9,Ffollowing a serious collision.
OL,11,FPolice were called at around 12.20pm
OL,12,Ffollowing reports of a two vehicle
OL,13,Fcollision.
OL,15,FA closure has been put into place
OL,16,Fbetween the junctions while emergency
OL,17,Fservices are at the scene. They are
OL,18,Fexpected to remain in place for a
OL,19,Fnumber of hours.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
